e minute it arrived I put it on. I could not believe how fast it started working. My coworker who sits behind me wanted to try a patch and it also worked for him. I was doubtful about this product, but after trying it and getting relief from my pain, I will continue to order this product.","reviewer_name":"Brenda","review_title":"Best thing yet!","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/person-stands-on-a-bridge-with-one-hand-on-each-railing.jpg"}},"image_anHXH9":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"I have pain in my wrists and arms from working at a desk and computer job. Decided to take a chance and order the patches. The product arrived really quickly... the next day! I put two patches on each arm and was able to notice a difference in the pain level. I saw some reviews that mentioned patches sticking to the sheet and being unusable. This was not the case with my order. I have not had any issues with the patches.","reviewer_name":"Matt","review_title":"Fast Delivery. Easy to use.","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/man-views-water.jpg"}},"image_8DpWTD":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"This cream is unbelievable. We use it for everything. My 14 year old son plays tennis every day and sometimes will get Tennis elbow. We just rub a little bit of this cream and his pain goes away. Also, I use this after I’m done exercising for my back, and it makes it so that I can sleep through the night. We have tried a lot of creams, but this is the best!","reviewer_name":"THAYNE G.","review_title":"AMAZING","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/portrait-young-man-smiling.jpg"}},"image_AAAfTD":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"I am on meds for my severe arthritis pain, but I still have severe pain almost daily due to my back, ankles & knees. They had to reduce my pain meds due to sleep apnea, which made my pain worse. So, I took matters into my own hands and started using cbd Patches. It has been about 4 months and my pain has been reduced drastically! I wish I didn’t have to pay cash for the patches, but the amount of relief I get is worth it. I am still slowly increasing my dose, but I am sleeping better and starting to go out more again since I’m not in debilitating pain.","reviewer_name":"ANA","review_title":"Pain Relief!","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/couple-sitting-on-couch-with-coffees.jpg"}},"image_Hf8W3p":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"I tried these patches on my neck and got lasting relief without the need to take harmful and addicting pain medications. My son also was diagnosed with an 11 mm disc bulge and often complains of low back pain interfering with a good night of sleep, but thanks to these patches, he has been able to move more and exercise. Plan to have them at home.","reviewer_name":"Tony","review_title":"Amazing Product","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/customer6.jpg"}},"image_wMd3pi":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"I am very impressed by these patches. Have had more relief from these than anything else I have tried over the last 10 years! While they don't take away all the pain, they reduce it by at least 50 percent. I have been using them for 24 hours each time I place a patch on my back. My only hope is that they will continue to provide relief as I continue to use them. I will be ordering more in the near future!","reviewer_name":"LAURA S","review_title":"Ordered 120 mg patches","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/woman-with-arms-crossed-smiling.jpg"}},"image_k9LJda":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"The patches are small and are the easiest of all patches that I have used and usually last 24 hours. Fabulous~!","reviewer_name":"Lorraine","review_title":"These really stop pain.","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gifts-for-65-years-old-women.jpg"}},"image_dyf64g":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"Some of them have a little figure in the patch helps me on the product sheet. Some don’t they have been giving me much needed pain relief between 12 And 20 hours. I will be a loyal user for some time. I have never been this pain free in two years Excellent product","reviewer_name":"Pauline","review_title":"Surprising an excellent product","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/images.jpg"}},"image_Q4QVc6":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"Easy to use, effective and no smell! As someone rather sensitive to strong scents I was concerned about this.","reviewer_name":"Amy","review_title":"Worth every penny","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/maxresdefault.jpg"}},"image_gcX8wC":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"After a month from my surgery dates I applied 3 patches to my collar bone area, outside shoulder area and upper bicep area. I noticed within 15 minutes that my nagging pain, which was worse at night had started to lighten. I would recommend.","reviewer_name":"Barry","review_title":"I would recommend.","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/depositphotos_259898524-stock-photo-portrait-old-man-arms-crossed.jpg"}},"image_d7AQwP":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"I honestly wasn't sure, they are tiny little stickers like scotch tape. I was desperate and thought I would try it....i was AMAZED how awesome they were and how much they worked. They make the biggest difference.","reviewer_name":"Sherry","review_title":"Amazing!","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/summer-fashion-model-smiles-in-the-park.jpg"}},"image_NMdLew":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"Got these for my mom because of her knee pain. She raved about them. She likes how they stay on when she moves or showers. Definetley helped her joint pain.","reviewer_name":"Suzy","review_title":"Mother approved","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/unnamed.jpg"}},"image_CnYY7g":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"The relief I have with this product is wonderful. It is actually more effective, in relieving lower back pain, than the steroid injections that Pain Specialists have given me AND NO negative side effects!","reviewer_name":"Terry","review_title":"No side effects","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/700-00350904en_Masterfile-400x301.jpg"}},"image_CiFWpi":{"type":"image","settings":{"review":"This product is FANTASTIC! I can't say enough good things about these patches. Do they work? YES!! Is it worth the price? YES!!! I put them anywhere I have pain or soreness and it goes away, quickly and seemlessly.","reviewer_name":"Todd","review_title":"Instant relief","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/silhoutted-hiker-at-mountain-peak.jpg"}}},"block_order":["image_Pzqbdn","image_JTQrPQ","image_anHXH9","image_8DpWTD","image_AAAfTD","image_Hf8W3p","image_wMd3pi","image_k9LJda","image_dyf64g","image_Q4QVc6","image_gcX8wC","image_d7AQwP","image_NMdLew","image_CnYY7g","image_CiFWpi"],"settings":{}},"section_2":{"type":"section_2","blocks":{"27f0eb60-4209-4e6a-9e52-64b451d49599":{"type":"slide","settings":{"custom_title":"Pain Relief Patches (8 mg ea.)","product":"pain-relief-patches"}},"f2bafb9e-bcb5-4028-bd9d-a0c3fa46954e":{"type":"slide","settings":{"custom_title":"GOLD Pain Relief Patches (24 mg ea.)","product":"hemp-relief-patches-gold"}},"d886dad0-1a2c-48b6-b2b2-d6307b604c3a":{"type":"slide","settings":{"custom_title":"Calm + Relax Nighttime Capsules (25 mg ea.)","product":"calm-relax"}},"f7c5f9fe-0a2b-49a1-8cbd-b15f32ebdc58":{"type":"slide","settings":{"custom_title":"Hot + Cool Pain Relief Cream (1,000 mg ea.)","product":"pain-relief-cream"}}},"block_order":["27f0eb60-4209-4e6a-9e52-64b451d49599","f2bafb9e-bcb5-4028-bd9d-a0c3fa46954e","d886dad0-1a2c-48b6-b2b2-d6307b604c3a","f7c5f9fe-0a2b-49a1-8cbd-b15f32ebdc58"],"settings":{"button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/product-catalog"}},"main__banner":{"type":"main__banner","settings":{}},"main__products":{"type":"main__products","blocks":{"131a2269-bb27-4498-83f1-1cd0f2193b53":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/CBD_Pain_Relief_Patches_15_ct._120_mg.png","custom_title":"8 mg Pain Relief Patch","product":"pain-relief-patches"}},"0c107953-69bd-467e-9348-3112bea535a3":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopif